b8ef790b-fca5-4aca-998b-49af25e0f850.title: Ava
b8ef790b-fca5-4aca-998b-49af25e0f850.text:
Hello there, I'm busy with my research. Come back in a
bit, could you?

8f76d518-3844-4322-934f-f91b245fbeef.title: Ava
8f76d518-3844-4322-934f-f91b245fbeef.text:
Hello there and welcome to my humble abode. It's sadly
rather more humble than I'd like, to be honest, although
perhaps you can help with that?

options.text: I would be happy to make your home a better place.
I'm not much into interior design, to tell the truth.
What's a nice girl like you doing in a place like this?

23ca5238-bf85-4f67-b0ab-1c0d7f4fcf16.title: <player>
23ca5238-bf85-4f67-b0ab-1c0d7f4fcf16.text: What's a nice girl like you doing in a place like this?

bf1b0ad4-95d3-4768-ab9c-1767e2d9b93e.title: Ava
bf1b0ad4-95d3-4768-ab9c-1767e2d9b93e.text:
I'm not a nice girl, I'm a respectable scientist
researching the interactions between ghosts and the
forces of pure science.

1ca96d7b-6400-468b-8958-a0c8fb1a299a.title: Ava
1ca96d7b-6400-468b-8958-a0c8fb1a299a.text:
I took over the position of assistant to the Professor
upstairs, although, to be honest, his methods are
somewhat eccentric. Did you hear about that Ernest
scandal?

670098ae-f233-4c42-9577-06fd1c225f44.title: <player>
670098ae-f233-4c42-9577-06fd1c225f44.text: Ahh yes, I helped sort that out; he did seem a bit odd.

ab855ba4-6d8e-412e-8f5c-0a723d7f64e0.title: Note
ab855ba4-6d8e-412e-8f5c-0a723d7f64e0.text: Different dialogue depending on ernest quest

f5dbdf62-8658-42dd-a873-16cb0f482e68.title: Ava
f5dbdf62-8658-42dd-a873-16cb0f482e68.text:
You don't know the half of it - can you believe that he
thinks he has proven Goldbach's First Conjecture using
an optimised segmented sieve?

7ae716d1-2102-4fbf-bd9b-7fe5a21205bc.title: <player>
7ae716d1-2102-4fbf-bd9b-7fe5a21205bc.text: I'm not much into interior design, to tell the truth.

1cf5c8c8-7f58-498b-9928-9a51c629170b.title: Ava
1cf5c8c8-7f58-498b-9928-9a51c629170b.text:
Very well, I suppose I'll just have to resort to the
Professor's patented sleeping aid in order to get some
rest. It does so bruise my head, though.

5ebc4cfc-2a9b-42ca-996a-c80ac6a98b82.title: <player>
5ebc4cfc-2a9b-42ca-996a-c80ac6a98b82.text: I would be happy to make your home a better place.

fd002056-4f8a-4604-9e69-5c824173e43b.title: Ava
fd002056-4f8a-4604-9e69-5c824173e43b.text:
I'm sorry, you need to complete The Restless Ghost
before I can use your help.

323b760c-91dd-43e2-a0f1-d0bd90bb53a4.title: Ava
323b760c-91dd-43e2-a0f1-d0bd90bb53a4.text:
I'm sorry, you need to complete Ernest the Chicken
before I can use your help.

f7edd606-f8b0-4eda-9ec1-954bca98836b.title: Ava
f7edd606-f8b0-4eda-9ec1-954bca98836b.text:
I'm sorry, you need to complete Priest in Peril
before I can use your help.

7bcd60e9-669e-4dec-ad54-bab332c3f46d.title: Ava
7bcd60e9-669e-4dec-ad54-bab332c3f46d.text:
I'm sorry, you need to have more skill in Slayer
before I can use your help.

5c8db389-82dc-42d8-a852-32279e2869b3.title: Ava
5c8db389-82dc-42d8-a852-32279e2869b3.text:
I'm sorry, you need to have more skill in Crafting
before I can use your help.

bab5c0b9-a8e9-4178-b8c3-38af21895e31.title: Ava
bab5c0b9-a8e9-4178-b8c3-38af21895e31.text:
I'm sorry, you need to have more skill in Ranged
before I can use your help.

8feba616-7aec-4552-a421-5cddce5760a8.title: Ava
8feba616-7aec-4552-a421-5cddce5760a8.text:
I'm sorry, you need to have more skill in Woodcutting
before I can use your help.

03e1b090-f5b6-4eb9-b58f-1a3ec54e5bbc.title: Ava
03e1b090-f5b6-4eb9-b58f-1a3ec54e5bbc.text:
Yay, I didn't even have to talk about a reward; you're
more gullible than most adventurers, that's for sure.

866a6c92-9ccc-4ac2-8a82-596c54d0b8cd.title: Ava
866a6c92-9ccc-4ac2-8a82-596c54d0b8cd.text:
Don't worry, though; I just need you to help fix this
vile old bed for me. Then I'll find a suitable reward for
you.

066467f4-5370-4fa1-a34c-fec39e57a66a.title: <player>
066467f4-5370-4fa1-a34c-fec39e57a66a.text: Great, will I be able to take a nap in it?

3da34330-088a-437e-9ad4-3dd635570bd2.title: Ava
3da34330-088a-437e-9ad4-3dd635570bd2.text:
Don't be silly; everyone knows that true warriors don't
ever sleep...or perform many other bodily functions, for
that matter. I'll come up with something, though.

52365603-3b0a-4e63-9047-e7851e2ea0cb.title: <player>
52365603-3b0a-4e63-9047-e7851e2ea0cb.text:
I'm not convinced by just a vague something; can you
be a slight bit more inspiring in your offer?

a50d53ff-57ea-4676-811f-8a9b6f12f84d.title: Ava
a50d53ff-57ea-4676-811f-8a9b6f12f84d.text:
What I need is simple: a couple of undead chickens.
You should be able to pick some up at the farm near
Port Phasmatys.

46f6e5e6-fe69-412f-8e82-53585eb3a1d3.title: Ava
46f6e5e6-fe69-412f-8e82-53585eb3a1d3.text:
I'll use one for my bed, then see what I can make
from the other in the way of a reward. I have some
ideas involving infinite feathers.

4e314cba-15d9-4ca0-9a9c-158100c7e6fc.title: <player>
4e314cba-15d9-4ca0-9a9c-158100c7e6fc.text:
Very well then, I shall await my mystery prize with
bated breath.

430982d0-af79-4ccd-81b2-319ef6727b58.title: Ava
430982d0-af79-4ccd-81b2-319ef6727b58.text:
Do you need a reminder what you are supposed to do?
I know you must have shiny beads distracting you, but
it is an important job you are doing for me.

options.text: No, thank you, I just came to gossip with you.

e4c2e0e5-5cb7-4bdf-ab45-079d126414f1.title: Ava
e4c2e0e5-5cb7-4bdf-ab45-079d126414f1.text: ...And people say we scientists are absent minded...

a7f1d988-63ab-4912-8293-cb40b59de87a.title: Ava
a7f1d988-63ab-4912-8293-cb40b59de87a.text:
You need to fetch 2 undead chickens for me to use in
my redecoration. It's not rocket science.

ef782ce8-3e29-491c-b366-c13971526c85.title: Ava
ef782ce8-3e29-491c-b366-c13971526c85.text:
If they existed, they would be like arrows but much,
much bigger. Considering the mess you rangers make
with small bits of stick, we scientists have decided they
don't exist. Now get chicken hunting.

0bb9d1f5-25cc-4e56-ad2f-6df75ed913d9.title: <player>
0bb9d1f5-25cc-4e56-ad2f-6df75ed913d9.text: No thank you; I just came to gossip with you.

ccb8cd5a-493e-48c2-887a-39abe19943f1.title: Ava
ccb8cd5a-493e-48c2-887a-39abe19943f1.text:
Well, the Witch next door has been cooking some rather
nice gingerbread, but I don't think that counts as
gossip.

c7d310ff-caea-4df4-9700-8bbe6b200e85.title: Ava
c7d310ff-caea-4df4-9700-8bbe6b200e85.text:
Can you head off and do adventurous stuff, please? I
hear the Wilderness is fun this time of year.

a671d6b1-2194-4c36-8353-9e2c802d3db1.title: Ava
a671d6b1-2194-4c36-8353-9e2c802d3db1.text:
How is the quest going? I could really do with a good
night's sleep, you know.

b4fc8461-f280-4268-91f8-015c747cc3b7.title: <player>
b4fc8461-f280-4268-91f8-015c747cc3b7.text:
I'm working on it - not that quickly, admittedly - but
I'll get around to it eventually.

229d574b-fb68-4721-a92a-5ebb3e38d463.title: Ava
229d574b-fb68-4721-a92a-5ebb3e38d463.text:
A typical adventurer. Your honesty is refreshing but
the cause of science can't be delayed by your inane
chatting about lobsters in Catherby. Hop to it!

71d3b438-91e1-4eee-b4d4-617356cc0001.title: <player>
71d3b438-91e1-4eee-b4d4-617356cc0001.text: Here's the second one for my reward.

3533bd0f-64aa-4b39-9763-8613eadbe3fc.title: <player>
3533bd0f-64aa-4b39-9763-8613eadbe3fc.text:
Well, I can buy the ones you want but I don't have
any on me.

f8f19527-592e-4991-8cf2-eea0a009ab27.title: Ava
f8f19527-592e-4991-8cf2-eea0a009ab27.text:
Stunning. I should have tried to hire some gnomes
instead. They may be obsessed with their bellies but
they can at least be trusted to deliver unpleasant
perishables.

83d73da5-dc01-4ac4-83a1-d9461c2b0ebf.title: Ava
83d73da5-dc01-4ac4-83a1-d9461c2b0ebf.text:
My spiritometric devices show that you have been in
close contact with ghostly animals. Are we closer to
success?

1a4091bc-673c-479f-ae53-1c090c6c2a7b.title: Ava
1a4091bc-673c-479f-ae53-1c090c6c2a7b.text:
Thanks! This is great for me, although I'll need another
one if you want any sort of reward.

90453d19-4d26-42fe-83d6-34639101ce28.title: Ava
90453d19-4d26-42fe-83d6-34639101ce28.text:
Amazing! Success! I can look forward to some good
nights' sleep after all.

4a54a654-48ef-4993-b049-01217f7919b8.title: <player>
4a54a654-48ef-4993-b049-01217f7919b8.text:
Can I ask exactly how an undead chicken will help you
sleep?

b3941d65-4ba4-4d6f-b260-e4d27c192973.title: Ava
b3941d65-4ba4-4d6f-b260-e4d27c192973.text:
Well, I need the feathers to make my bed more
comfortable. A comfortable bed will help me sleep.
Obvious, really.

03f3bb12-c8a7-4fde-882c-ead15ba06e2e.title: <player>
03f3bb12-c8a7-4fde-882c-ead15ba06e2e.text:
Obvious, yes, but why on Gielinor would you need an
undead chicken when there are perfectly good live
chickens just down the road?

e6f02fd7-d652-4060-8584-bd6c563c09e6.title: Ava
e6f02fd7-d652-4060-8584-bd6c563c09e6.text:
Well, for a start, undead feathers are much cleaner
than living ones; no dust mites or anything. Secondly, I
always think of Ernest when I see a chicken, so my
nerves can't take killing them.

fcec1105-7642-401c-b0f1-7a2306af5b77.title: <player>
fcec1105-7642-401c-b0f1-7a2306af5b77.text:
Then why do I need a chicken for my reward; we
already established that I don't use a bed?

62391268-6c1b-4726-81c7-24875656c70e.title: Ava
62391268-6c1b-4726-81c7-24875656c70e.text:
Seeing as how you ranger types use so many feathers
in your arrows, I was thinking I could harness an
undead chicken to make an unending supply of arrow
flights for you.

94023ec0-c45f-4f03-a69e-0eea85818e97.title: <player>
94023ec0-c45f-4f03-a69e-0eea85818e97.text:
Beats chicken slaying or hanging around in fishing
shops, I suppose. So, what next?

df1b2d86-8541-475d-ad03-7f0630971759.title: Ava
df1b2d86-8541-475d-ad03-7f0630971759.text:
We'll need a magnet next, one with purely natural
fields and made from a carefully selected iron bar. A
firm impact when the iron is parallel to Gielinor's field
will stabilise this field in the rod.

c02665ac-e8fb-4970-9992-3741359a2886.title: Ava
c02665ac-e8fb-4970-9992-3741359a2886.text: Go and talk to the Witch next door.

85737466-7cf4-4b10-b425-d2620f3fe8b9.title: Ava
85737466-7cf4-4b10-b425-d2620f3fe8b9.text:
Go and talk to the Witch next door. She'd talk the hind
legs off a donkey but she can select the iron with which
it is suitable for the chicken to interact.

dba47ea3-aadb-4988-a618-d70fdf2e4d18.title: Ava
dba47ea3-aadb-4988-a618-d70fdf2e4d18.text:
Despite my extensive studies, her years of experience
make her better at instinctive magico-mystical
interaction. Oh well, at least I'm cleverer, prettier and
will have a better bed.

161090f4-1c56-4355-b36f-29f6300b6d64.title: <player>
161090f4-1c56-4355-b36f-29f6300b6d64.text:
Okay, okay, you're great. Yes, I'll go and talk to her
when you've finished praising yourself.

88cc1908-4e6c-4612-af6b-8e0a8a36746d.title: <player>
88cc1908-4e6c-4612-af6b-8e0a8a36746d.text:
I've talked to the Witch and she has asked me for some
iron bars.

d196e20e-9460-4d17-a2b0-266a749a1893.title: Ava
d196e20e-9460-4d17-a2b0-266a749a1893.text: Do I resemble an iron-bar merchant?

c216ffcc-1491-4ec8-8692-f7b8215fbb9e.title: <player>
c216ffcc-1491-4ec8-8692-f7b8215fbb9e.text: Er, maybe; I've never met one.

44475a6b-6e43-4289-873c-7d45e8cb882c.title: Ava
44475a6b-6e43-4289-873c-7d45e8cb882c.text: An entirely logical answer; you'll make a scientist yet.

36524a2e-c9ce-4ca8-838d-6698d10212fc.title: <player>
36524a2e-c9ce-4ca8-838d-6698d10212fc.text:
I've talked to the Witch and now I've given her some
iron bars.

d556a395-9618-4a45-88c6-f4157aaf0ca8.title: Ava
d556a395-9618-4a45-88c6-f4157aaf0ca8.text: I'm thrilled for you. What about my magnet?

c9393fd8-3ec7-417d-8a84-f0cd7dac6195.title: <player>
c9393fd8-3ec7-417d-8a84-f0cd7dac6195.text: The process is subject to some unexpected delays.

38dd2f08-9e61-47f0-8967-fee9fa48382c.title: Ava
38dd2f08-9e61-47f0-8967-fee9fa48382c.text:
I can see now why Fenkenstrain prefers to work with
dead folk. It can't be more frustrating than working
with you.

9d28393c-82b3-4259-9503-0257049b8284.title: <player>
9d28393c-82b3-4259-9503-0257049b8284.text: I've manufactured the magnet; here it is.

6ed64afe-ce9d-4d46-8664-8ee4dc8de226.title: Ava
6ed64afe-ce9d-4d46-8664-8ee4dc8de226.text:
Great stuff! With the Witch's influence within the
magnet, the undead chicken can use this, I'm sure.

e3684901-c7e2-4347-89b9-a3a9ef04161a.title: Ava
e3684901-c7e2-4347-89b9-a3a9ef04161a.text:
The plan is that the chicken will operate the magnet to
attract bits of iron and steel, maybe even your own
recently fired arrows. There are plenty of totally lost
arrowheads lying about in the fields of Gielinor, I bet.

6e9f90aa-9b0e-4b42-8b40-ab939b4ceddb.title: Ava
6e9f90aa-9b0e-4b42-8b40-ab939b4ceddb.text:
In addition, arrows which you fire should be able to be
attracted back to your quiver by the cunning avian.

29121f7e-1ea4-45f7-981d-88f25407fb72.title: <player>
29121f7e-1ea4-45f7-981d-88f25407fb72.text:
I begin to understand your plan. We've covered
feathers and arrowheads now; what next?

e08e3973-c948-455f-a00d-f8bd6a92a0bf.title: Ava
e08e3973-c948-455f-a00d-f8bd6a92a0bf.text:
We need a source of wood, but one which is spiritually
active and can regenerate itself. That will save you
some axework in the future.

c649d09d-672e-4985-9d3f-984a7100ff28.title: Ava
c649d09d-672e-4985-9d3f-984a7100ff28.text:
Try using a woodcutting axe on the pesky trees in the
garden here, the ones that attack rather than the really
dead ones. They are probably just the sort of thing we
could use.

7dfc2a33-aa93-40e5-9a6f-0a603b52e04a.title: <player>
7dfc2a33-aa93-40e5-9a6f-0a603b52e04a.text: They will try to kill me, though, and I can't fight back!

bff4823a-2fe6-4431-8375-517ea6a6c26f.title: Ava
bff4823a-2fe6-4431-8375-517ea6a6c26f.text:
Now you know how those poor guards feel when you
hide behind mushrooms and fences and attack them
from afar! Anyway, I reckon you'll need to try a
mithril or better axe on the trees. At least the trees are

args: Your work with the magnet increases your Crafting experience slightly.

53f8d46a-042c-4922-ac19-fe70c0628774.title: Ava
53f8d46a-042c-4922-ac19-fe70c0628774.text: So, what terrible hitch have you encountered now?

3bd1df8c-c4c3-4fd7-974e-0427154c91de.title: <player>
3bd1df8c-c4c3-4fd7-974e-0427154c91de.text:
Nothing really; I just decided to talk to you in case
you have any great advice for me.

3118c664-c1c0-44a3-92b2-311baa8e2d75.title: Ava
3118c664-c1c0-44a3-92b2-311baa8e2d75.text:
Well, I've heard that all kinds of dragons and even
basilisks can drop mithril axes, if that's why you are
delaying. Most of these creatures are silly enough that
you can even hide behind something and plink them to

c2314797-ae70-4e3a-8e6f-1181c330ae95.title: Ava
c2314797-ae70-4e3a-8e6f-1181c330ae95.text: death in that brave ranger way.

ee45209e-9405-49b9-87a9-010789671acf.title: <player>
ee45209e-9405-49b9-87a9-010789671acf.text:
Well, I tried to hack the trees with my axe, but it just
bounced off the trunk! It did all seem all-too-convenient
to work on the first try.

245001ea-1cfa-424b-ad22-0298c7614625.title: Ava
245001ea-1cfa-424b-ad22-0298c7614625.text:
Fortunately for you, I've done some research and it
seems to suggest that there are two choices open to
you.

7a81eb41-d7dd-4e48-b8b2-b861fc196eca.title: Ava
7a81eb41-d7dd-4e48-b8b2-b861fc196eca.text:
The first is more interesting. We cut off your arms,
have them reanimated as undead, reattach them and
then you should be able to cut the trees normally.

df651a8e-aed9-4844-b2da-380f25074c39.title: Ava
df651a8e-aed9-4844-b2da-380f25074c39.text:
Of course, you won't be able to pick your nose any
more, so I suppose you'll want to try the second option.

4c4e6700-b9ca-4d6b-87f9-40d1e25d6e9d.title: <player>
4c4e6700-b9ca-4d6b-87f9-40d1e25d6e9d.text:
I'm not exactly addicted to picking my nose, but I do
think I'll pass on that method.

6cacd183-9b0d-41ef-865d-53a4b9573fc5.title: Ava
6cacd183-9b0d-41ef-865d-53a4b9573fc5.text:
Well, in that case, I think it may have something to do
with Slayer abilities. After all, I did see Turael poking
around the trees while I was moving in.

c11b4af5-7b32-49ed-b931-90acd0bcf5a5.title: Ava
c11b4af5-7b32-49ed-b931-90acd0bcf5a5.text:
As he's not known for his random touristic activities,
you should try chatting with this Turael. He's the
Slayer Master near Burthorpe.

df8d126e-8e11-4aef-8d1b-90224037d657.title: <player>
df8d126e-8e11-4aef-8d1b-90224037d657.text:
Oh dear, I hope he doesn't want me to buy one of his
ridiculous fashion accessories. Those earmuffs he sells
make heroic adventurers into a laughing stock.

8be9174e-4a17-4435-b5ad-907e41f33428.title: <player>
8be9174e-4a17-4435-b5ad-907e41f33428.text:
Turael, the Slayer Master, told me what to do - with no
earmuffs, spiky helmets or other laughable headgear
involved.

32bf7bb9-a20b-48e1-81bf-2165ba9d0438.title: Ava
32bf7bb9-a20b-48e1-81bf-2165ba9d0438.text:
A pity; you'd look quite cute with rabbit ears. Perhaps I
should have bribed him.

4b3333fc-01df-40cd-b7d8-4902ea5036e4.title: <player>
4b3333fc-01df-40cd-b7d8-4902ea5036e4.text: I think I'm ready to cut those trees now.

91d4ca96-cb3c-4e43-8d05-6f2d9d8a77a6.title: Ava
91d4ca96-cb3c-4e43-8d05-6f2d9d8a77a6.text:
What do you want? A prize? Go and get the wood; it's
not as if the trees are wandering about and hard to
find.

b2d8540a-8862-4dc9-816a-9f532e1e72be.title: <player>
b2d8540a-8862-4dc9-816a-9f532e1e72be.text: I have that undead wood at last. Well, twigs anyway.

be875796-0669-49d7-9bf6-ef1fa79d532e.title: <player>
be875796-0669-49d7-9bf6-ef1fa79d532e.text:
I'd say they didn't grow on trees, but I guess you'd
just be sarcastic about my sense of humour.

e601dfcc-e391-46f0-b2d3-8e0adc99289e.title: Ava
e601dfcc-e391-46f0-b2d3-8e0adc99289e.text:
Quite. Now that we have all the ingredients for infinite
arrows, we just need a container in which we can keep
the components in the correct mutual alignment.

074bf3c1-2807-476e-9b46-49aeae1d2592.title: Ava
074bf3c1-2807-476e-9b46-49aeae1d2592.text:
I've gathered together some research notes from various
sources but I can't quite make out what they mean. If
you want to have a go at making them out, just ask me
for a copy.

4276c92e-ee21-4e71-98c8-f68d21065fb2.title: <player>
4276c92e-ee21-4e71-98c8-f68d21065fb2.text:
I'd like to look at those research notes now, unless you
have translated them without me?

cac84b85-79ed-4585-98da-14bce9c2b55c.title: Ava
cac84b85-79ed-4585-98da-14bce9c2b55c.text:
They are still stumping me. Here are the notes; I
really hope your head doesn't explode from reading
them.

9b7ce9a8-5391-499f-9a86-277d7fa23f50.title: <player>
9b7ce9a8-5391-499f-9a86-277d7fa23f50.text: I'd find it slightly inconvenient, I'm sure.

44ad2159-4878-4520-bd27-b20a2966bf44.title: Ava
44ad2159-4878-4520-bd27-b20a2966bf44.text:
It wouldn't be all bad as your body would be useful for
research after death. What I'd be upset about was if
bits of you landed in my nice new bed.

faee3e10-8a97-4ae5-9428-fbc56d6dee4c.title: <player>
faee3e10-8a97-4ae5-9428-fbc56d6dee4c.text:
I've translated those notes. See? I'm not just a thuggish
moron like you seem to think.

956fb009-2980-4416-9762-91a979b9bf46.title: Ava
956fb009-2980-4416-9762-91a979b9bf46.text:
For all I know, it was pure luck, so don't jump to any
conclusions about your mighty intellect.

7476309c-3fdd-4dbf-ae0c-a377e860c794.title: <player>
7476309c-3fdd-4dbf-ae0c-a377e860c794.text:
I can see why you don't have any assistants; you're
not exactly easy to work with.

74e8ea5b-c0d9-4e85-ad00-a086d6156406.title: Ava
74e8ea5b-c0d9-4e85-ad00-a086d6156406.text:
Let's get back to the work we're doing, then.
Remember, this is all a favour to you; I could have just
decided to fob you off with a feather duster.

dae5b06f-8143-42de-a9b9-76e96c2898c7.title: Ava
dae5b06f-8143-42de-a9b9-76e96c2898c7.text:
I've given you a pattern for the container; you'll need
to combine them with some polished buttons and hard
leather. Then we're almost done. Good news, eh?

01bbbe63-8bb3-4497-98b7-49705257a0c8.title: Ava
01bbbe63-8bb3-4497-98b7-49705257a0c8.text:
If you are having trouble finding buttons, I've heard
rumours that the H.A.M. society carry this sort of stuff
more than most.

dfcac62c-664e-43d9-88a0-111aeee83b8b.title: <player>
dfcac62c-664e-43d9-88a0-111aeee83b8b.text: Really? How would you know this strange detail?

6cc98de7-fdfc-4263-bdf5-e22c3995dba2.title: Ava
6cc98de7-fdfc-4263-bdf5-e22c3995dba2.text:
I hear they lose their clothes a lot to thieves so they
have to make do with shoddy goods. Whatever the
reason, they seem to carry buttons about in their
pockets.

481368fc-eb19-41b1-8460-3a53e0099a66.title: <player>
481368fc-eb19-41b1-8460-3a53e0099a66.text:
I've translated those notes. See? I'm not just a thuggish
moron like you seem to think.

bbab690f-d848-47fd-91ea-3a84ef2b8b64.title: Ava
bbab690f-d848-47fd-91ea-3a84ef2b8b64.text:
I know you have the notes; I gave them to you, in case
you forgot! Furthermore, if I had hints, I'd have
translated those notes myself.

34435779-822b-41c9-a1d5-7c9bc81277ea.title: Ava
34435779-822b-41c9-a1d5-7c9bc81277ea.text:
So, take the hint and go off and translate them. If it's
too hard, you can always go and shoot demons in
cages.

463e20ed-b993-4b2b-b9d3-a25c2ac1efd4.title: <player>
463e20ed-b993-4b2b-b9d3-a25c2ac1efd4.text: I seem to have lost the research notes.

a6a65dd9-aaeb-40aa-ba72-d93e85d8a772.title: Ava
a6a65dd9-aaeb-40aa-ba72-d93e85d8a772.text:
Don't tell me, your cat ate them? You won't get out of
the job that easily; here are some copies I made.

d16a7429-dc3c-46d7-b14e-5333eb003821.title: <player>
d16a7429-dc3c-46d7-b14e-5333eb003821.text: So what do I do with this pattern again?

03a60e57-c50a-4e43-b425-6853d86325a0.title: Ava
03a60e57-c50a-4e43-b425-6853d86325a0.text:
Your short-term memory loss worries me. Combine the
pattern with hard leather and some polished buttons,
then hand the resulting container to me.

adf6606f-ff4a-4aab-805a-1dd61e598b66.title: <player>
adf6606f-ff4a-4aab-805a-1dd61e598b66.text:
The pattern seems to have vanished from my pack...not
my fault, of course.

9d87f467-d703-46e9-82cd-935a01daf281.title: Ava
9d87f467-d703-46e9-82cd-935a01daf281.text:
You're pretty careless, aren't you. I assume you're the
type who leaves a trail of arrows and knives behind
them when they train?

0dbab912-83cb-495c-a3e9-2c0006ed5e43.title: Ava
0dbab912-83cb-495c-a3e9-2c0006ed5e43.text:
Here's a replacement; perhaps if I charged for them,
you'd be more careful.

daf8b149-8f7f-44f3-834c-37b5410e9210.title: Ava
daf8b149-8f7f-44f3-834c-37b5410e9210.text: You've made the container, I assume?

54b13d57-9b72-4d92-9cfb-8375ade0f27a.title: <player>
54b13d57-9b72-4d92-9cfb-8375ade0f27a.text: Well, yes, although I seem to have mislaid it.

f1c173b0-c884-46de-97ad-f1c9321c3528.title: Ava
f1c173b0-c884-46de-97ad-f1c9321c3528.text:
It's only the final, vital step in your quest that you
decided to leave who-knows-where. Don't worry, I have
plenty of spares.

1cab9444-69ca-42db-aa31-4254291ef7c8.title: <player>
1cab9444-69ca-42db-aa31-4254291ef7c8.text: Why do I sense sarcasm somewhere here?

3107df67-5985-4815-a8df-d9e586949786.title: Ava
3107df67-5985-4815-a8df-d9e586949786.text:
Wow, great, now the arrow manufacturer is ready for
use...there you are! Talk to me if you need more
information later.

b8e85349-d0d1-42f3-8a1e-c63e570efad4.title: Ava
b8e85349-d0d1-42f3-8a1e-c63e570efad4.text:
Hello again. Are you after an upgrade to your device,
or a new device, or some information, or would you like
to see my goods for sale?

options.text: I'd like to see your stuff for sale, please.
I'll just head off, I think.

61d21922-89fb-4121-b596-7f4b0f9179b2.title: Ava
61d21922-89fb-4121-b596-7f4b0f9179b2.text:
Just a few bits of information before you run away to
persecute rock crabs or cows.

f51bf242-e57c-4ada-8a78-48a05a8b02c2.title: Ava
f51bf242-e57c-4ada-8a78-48a05a8b02c2.text:
Firstly, your new device won't work if you are wearing
certain metallic chest armours.

1b9f22bd-2a08-4b85-b72f-17b576535793.title: Ava
1b9f22bd-2a08-4b85-b72f-17b576535793.text:
The magnetic attraction required for operation would
cause feedback, so the device does not allow such
incompatible item equippage.

34aeafc8-1f1c-4f0f-8ddd-82ca2f7eebde.title: Ava
34aeafc8-1f1c-4f0f-8ddd-82ca2f7eebde.text:
Secondly, although the device is calibrated to attract
only arrow heads, there is a chance that other
magnetically active items will be attracted.

84b6ae02-bd5f-4130-8a02-1c7d416a4b4c.title: Ava
84b6ae02-bd5f-4130-8a02-1c7d416a4b4c.text:
The arrow recovery function of the devices is slightly
different and relies upon a harmonic bond between
your arrows and the chicken's magnet. You'll thus only
recover arrows which you have fired rather than those

53e0fcc7-bb28-495f-abb3-68d204f6ac34.title: Ava
53e0fcc7-bb28-495f-abb3-68d204f6ac34.text:
Thirdly, there is an upgraded version available when
your Ranged level is 50 or greater, so visit me when
you have had more practice.

5fb2b5e9-3504-4fed-9d94-b79541650762.title: Ava
5fb2b5e9-3504-4fed-9d94-b79541650762.text:
You'll also need to move about if you want to collect
arrows since the gathering of long-lost arrowheads can't
work otherwise.

b4e8ae2b-e9a8-42b8-8357-22a9b6d1fa84.title: Ava
b4e8ae2b-e9a8-42b8-8357-22a9b6d1fa84.text:
Finally, the device will only work when worn. It
automatically deactivates in other circumstances.

be7c1aed-2639-4b78-a2ba-b70b67876b6e.title: Ava
be7c1aed-2639-4b78-a2ba-b70b67876b6e.text:
I was worried about what would happen if you were to
place it in a bank in its active state, so I've made sure
it only works when it's on your back.

03d9893f-73af-465a-b4a8-a4b317a0d3c6.title: <player>
03d9893f-73af-465a-b4a8-a4b317a0d3c6.text: I'd like to see your stuff for sale, please.

0b9d71df-4c1c-49b0-a55a-d70121ce07ed.title: <player>
0b9d71df-4c1c-49b0-a55a-d70121ce07ed.text: I'll just head off, I think.

7cc48bbf-adbb-4cae-b418-e0ec0a6ceeed.title: Ava
7cc48bbf-adbb-4cae-b418-e0ec0a6ceeed.text: Thanks for the help with my bed; see you again.
